name: The HEN World - Where Everything Is Possible
description: Free-hand mandala sketch, with pencil and markers. 'The HEN World - Where Everything Is Possible' piece was done in commemoration to the first 100 days of H=N's inception.  The four circles represent four aspects, love & creation, frequency, yin & yang and H=N.  This is Hic Et Nunc.  Here. Now. Forever.
